body:
Currently, Dubbo does not support the transmission of big files,  you can use [hessian protocol instead](http://dubbo.apache.org/#!/docs/user/references/protocol/hessian.md?lang=zh-cn). Hessian allows you can define an interface looks like this:
```java
public File findFileById(String id);
public InputStream findFileById(String id);
```

@zhouyuzhy

If the call failed, it will join the failure list and retry it. If the retry is successful, it will be removed.
Test code can be provided ?  This issue can be reopened at any time.
